    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The exterior has multiple large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on the rocker panels. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and there is a noticeable leak from the transmission. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is a project car best suited for someone looking for parts or a complete restoration.",
